Package frc.robot.BreakerLib.util

Class BreakerArbitraryFeedforwardProvider

java.lang.Object
frc.robot.BreakerLib.util.BreakerArbitraryFeedforwardProvider
public class BreakerArbitraryFeedforwardProvider
extends java.lang.Object
A class that acts as a provider for arbitrary feedforward demand values used with the Talon or SparkMax motor controller's integrated PID.
